## Problem Lanes

- `formal_theorem_factory` -> `formal_proof_packet`: turn informal problem statement into formal target, proof attempt, checker output, and counterexample path
- `biomedical_mechanism_lab` -> `mechanism_claim_packet`: separate mechanism claim, assay evidence, intervention, endpoint, and negative evidence
- `protein_design_lab` -> `protein_receipt_packet`: bind sequence, structure, ligand, assay, and design claim without promotion leakage
- `robotics_generalization_lab` -> `robotics_benchmark_packet`: join policy, simulator, dataset, benchmark, code, and real-world evaluation receipts
- `climate_resilience_lab` -> `climate_model_packet`: bind spatial grid, temporal window, dataset version, model assumption, and uncertainty receipt
- `materials_discovery_lab` -> `materials_property_packet`: join composition, structure, calculation method, property, synthesis evidence, and unit receipts
- `ai_model_benchmark_lab` -> `ai_benchmark_packet`: bind dataset card, model card, eval script, metric, run environment, and failure cases
- `clinical_translation_lab` -> `clinical_translation_packet`: distinguish trial registry facts, publication facts, outcome claims, and approval claims
- `college_knowledge_graph_lab` -> `institution_claim_graph`: join institution, lab, paper, dataset, code, and thesis claims
- `patent_prior_art_lab` -> `prior_art_packet`: join invention claim, prior art, assignee, paper, and implementation evidence
- `economic_policy_lab` -> `policy_claim_packet`: bind indicator provenance, time-series version, counterfactual boundary, and policy claim
- `scientific_runtime_lab` -> `scientific_runtime_packet`: bind source, compiler, runtime, numerical method, measurement, and verifier receipts

## Warning Policy

A failed probe is not source absence. Rate limits, query-shape failures, and service outages remain adapter work items until a later pass rejects them with evidence.

## Boundary

Pass 0151 federates source and problem-substrate routes. It does not prove complete global coverage, source truth, theorem resolution, experimental validity, clinical efficacy, market adoption, or a natural law.
